 {
  "date": "2016-01-13 14:55", 
  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p762781/", 
  "description": "<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/zt/bbclearningenglish/\" style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201507/c6e5c0306433433eb4a3dcf14ae6a467.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201601/58483c1e94144acdae5cca1cc64b90a6.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>今日短语</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t如果你设法打入了一个特殊的职业领域 to break into a particular career，那就说明你成功地迈出了新事业中的第一步，也就是获得了第一份工作。这个短语通常用来形容那种竞争力强、令人仰慕的职业。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>例句</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<em>He managed to break into acting after many years working as a waiter and doing amateur shows.</em></p>\n<p>\n\t<em>It&lsquo;s difficult, but not impossible, to break into brain surgery if you have the right skills and a lot of determination.</em></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>请注意</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tBreak into 这个短语的另一个意思是&ldquo;用强制手段进入某处&rdquo;。比如，一栋楼内或一辆汽车内。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>例句</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<em>Do you remember when you had to break into your car after you locked your keys inside?</em></p>\n<p>\n\t<em>He was arrested for breaking into the school to try and find the exam questions.</em></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201507/96d23c9b2d084a4e8c878ed4f9937b90.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; line-height: 25.2px;\">声明：&nbsp;本文由BBC英语教学授权沪江英语发布。任何媒体禁止转载。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p762781/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p762781\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762619/\">宝宝哭泣的40个理由：小孩的脑回路简直了！</a></li><li style=\"mar